```

Default local URL:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5173
```

Local workspace TypeScript dependencies update in the same dev session when they are workspace-linked (`workspace:`, `link:`, or `file:`) and imported from app code used by client or SSR render paths.

Expected SSR contract failures:

- Missing SSR entry module: `SSR contract error: failed to load /src/entry-server.ts: ...`
- Invalid SSR render export: `SSR contract error: /src/entry-server.ts must export a render(url) function`

Local dependency troubleshooting:

- If local dependency edits do not apply on SSR paths, verify `vite.config.ts` includes `ssr.noExternal` for workspace-linked dependency package names.
- If local dependency source resolves outside the app root, verify `vite.config.ts` keeps `server.fs.allow` scoped to the workspace root.
